Definition: any disease of the mind
Example: the psychological state of someone who has emotional or behavioral problems serious enough to require psychiatric intervention
Synonyms: mental_health, mental_disease, psychopathy, adj, all, insane, psychopathic, psychological_state, any, disease, of, the, mind, psychological, state, someone, who, has, emotional, or, behavioral, problems, serious, enough, to, require, psychiatric, intervention
Category: noun.state
